{"id":"d7b6da11ce799808f87e49fd83eafc939a023473916af9585ed48d5406884174","item_id":"102942bbb5:0","text":"RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.hip"}
{"id":"d071ac21d5c0e063c9253f71ddfcb231a8009b67f92b7a2093171e31621d115b","item_id":"102942bbb5:1","text":"此场景包含位于默认 layout（布局）中的所有 studio assets（影棚资产），可供你创建自己的场景。你可以通过"}
{"id":"9717a6115a56f8e46eb1a87597952285f418256594ef60e3098e0e35f45facef","item_id":"102942bbb5:2","text":"stagemanager（舞台管理器）"}
{"id":"928afc651f832a4383ea2d2e641316ea8a76d3e7fc681b6d31e75847d746bf32","item_id":"102942bbb5:3","text":"查看这些 USD assets（USD 资产）中有趣的 model variants（模型变体）和 shading variants（着色变体）。"}
{"id":"85e24b2e8d468c8d3bdf4f4adf53ce3f0a9a4dcdc3c74ed4d182647aa820c982","item_id":"102942bbb5:4","text":"场景中包含一台 camera（摄影机）和若干 lights（灯光），它们会生成你在下方看到的 render（渲染）。"}
{"id":"b344d80e24a3679999fa964450b34bc24d1578a35509f934c1418b0a20d21a67","item_id":"102942bbb5:5","text":"该"}
{"id":"8e84c0688cec29db07bf35ecaaf5ef7d437d3d1ed70b08e16d289973cc96102f","item_id":"102942bbb5:6","text":"usd_Assembly"}
{"id":"1403bc8eca3cf044192b555bffb993fb8d580d0d770823291cfa11c977b756a0","item_id":"102942bbb5:7","text":"USD ROP node（USD ROP 节点）用于将这个默认 layout（布局）保存到"}
{"id":"79832da23695c09f03552fb307d68a106f8c7d118722c5583188246917e2c235","item_id":"102942bbb5:8","text":"$HIP/usd/Assembly/RenderManStudio_Assembly_v01.usda -"}
{"id":"22d0afc2f0270edde7ef0b099df20d333538257d78c98c68d4f654e330f9260b","item_id":"102942bbb5:9","text":"该文件由 RenderManStudio_Layout_v01.hip 引用"}
{"id":"7d668e6c8c060f7820a4f1b517d9750ec4b9e171c42c13fa57c943892e6d8ee4","item_id":"102942bbb5:10","text":"你的浏览器不支持 HTML5 video element（HTML5 视频元素）"}
{"id":"f897c197a20a7489edaeaadb0ff6e7b511cce30bcc8cfe920935e9e2a129fcc0","item_id":"102942bbb5:11","text":"你可以随意将自己的 assets（资产）添加到 stage manager（舞台管理器），然后继续进入下一阶段，"}
